snippet.title: The Grumpy Geek
snippet.description:
This channel is dedicated to all things geeky, nerdy, and weird  from  comic books, movies, and TV, to videogames, and anything else that is considered a part of geek culture. Think of me like Morpheus, here to free your mind!

Dont forget to like, share, and subscribe!
